{{unreferenced|date=May 2016}} The '''1969 [[Mr. Olympia]]''' contest was an [[International Federation of BodyBuilders|IFBB]] [[professional bodybuilding]] competition held in September {{Citation needed|date=January 2013}} 1969 at the [[Brooklyn Academy of Music]] in [[Brooklyn]], [[New York (state)|New York]]. It was the 5th Mr. Olympia competition held.
