{{Infobox cycling race report | name = 2014 Omloop van het Hageland | image = | image_caption = | series = | race_no = | season_no = | date = 9 March 2014 | stages = 1 | distance = 122.3 | unit = km | time = 3h 15' 43" | speed = 37.4 | first = [[Lizzie Armitstead]] | first_nat = GBR | first_natvar = | first_team = {{ct|DLT|2014}} | second = [[Emma Johansson]] | second_nat = SWE | second_natvar = | second_team = [[Orica-AIS]] | third = [[Audrey Cordon]] | third_nat = FRA | third_natvar = | third_team = [[Hitec Products UCK]] | previous = [[2013 Omloop van het Hageland|2013]] | next = [[2015 Omloop van het Hageland|2015]] }} The '''2014 Omloop van het Hageland''' was the tenth running of the women's [[Omloop van het Hageland]], a [[List of women's road bicycle races|women's bicycle race]] in [[Belgium]]. It was held on 9 March 2014, over a distance of {{convert|122.3|km|1|abbr=off}} around [[Tielt-Winge]]. It was rated by the [[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] as a 1.2 category race.<ref name="PCS">http://www.procyclingstats.com/race/Omloop_van_het_Hageland_Tielt_Winge_2014</ref> The race was won by British rider [[Lizzie Armitstead]] of the {{ct|DLT|2014}}.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www1.skysports.com/cycling/news/15264/9204921/lizzie-armitstead-wins-omloop-van-het-hageland-one-day-race-in-belgium|title=Lizzie Armitstead wins Omloop van het Hageland one-day race in Belgium|work=[[Sky Sports]]|publisher=[[BSkyB]]|date=9 March 2014|accessdate=9 March 2014}}</ref>
