'''[[Qatar]]''' participated in the [[1998 Asian Games]] held in [[Bangkok]], [[Thailand]] from December 6, 1998 to December 20, 1998. Athletes from Qatar succeeded in winning two golds, three silvers and three bronzes, making total eight medals. Qatar finished eighteenth in a medal table.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.ocasia.org/Game/MWinner.aspx?AMWCode=17&GCode=1 | title=Over all medal standings &ndash; Bangkok 1998 | publisher=ocasia.org | work=[[Olympic Council of Asia]] | accessdate=June 6, 2011}}</ref>
